Package: Genomica
Title: Linear mixed model based, multiple hypothesis testing corrected, ortholog enrichment analysis.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Salvatore", "Galgano",, "salvatore.galgano@sruc.ac.uk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment=c(ORCID='0000-0002-5600-3206'))
Description: Genomica provides a suite to analyse complex genomic data of different origin, both from eucaryotic and procaryotic organisms (e.g., taxonomic or functional-gene tables from shotgun metagenomics, AMR tables or quantitative gene tables from qPCR experimnents). The only inputs required by the user are a data and a metadata files. If required, Genomica will carry out the log10 transformation of pre-normalised data. The final outputs are false discovery rate corrected  .xlsx files summarising the significant comparisons.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
